{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/9221", "repo": "rails", "body": "About the changelog.\r\nIt is wrong mentioning ```Apple Voice Over```\r\nBecause before it works bad with ``` Apple Voice Over ```, as said [here](http://www.w3schools.com/tags/att_img_alt.asp), the current implementation is violating the ```alt``` definition.\r\n\r\n* The text should describe the image if the image contains information\r\n* The text should explain where the link goes if the image is inside an ```<a>``` element\r\n* Use ```alt=\"\"``` if the image is only for decoration", "_id": {"$oid": "523d411fbd354364b9005b00"}, "issue_id": 9221, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/13328125", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/9221#issuecomment-13328125", "updated_at": "2013-02-09T08:32:55Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri", "login": "acapilleri", "gravatar_id": "0cd98f4e263d306bc455ca750c31443f", "html_url": "https://github.com/acapilleri", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/0cd98f4e263d306bc455ca750c31443f?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2e17b55bd1f302b773d04e4938adef85.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 46208, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/acapilleri/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2013-02-09T08:31:50Z", "id": 13328125, "owner": "rails"}
